{"tid":1130146,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[小島秀夫] 重新連結分裂的世界 《 Death Stranding 》一個多月後有新預告？","createTime":"2019-04-28T23:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T11:55:11.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f46ed85b6aceb5ad437ac55ed2161ac0dfd55f3","tid":1130146,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T23:53:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://greatgame.asia/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E3%80%8A-death-stranding-%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C-%25E3%2580%258A-death-stranding-%25E3%2580%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25A0%2590%25E5%2591%258A%2F&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9fvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=b4a64758\" target=\"_blank\">https://greatgame.asia/%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E9%80%A3%E7%B5%90%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E3%80%8A-death-stranding-%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%88%E5%BE%8C%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>重新連結分裂的世界 《 Death Stranding 》一個多月後有新預告？</strong><br />\n<br />\n日前於美國紐約市舉辦的Tribeca電影節，邀請了遊戲製作人小島秀夫，及擔任其作品《 Death Stranding 》男主角的荷里活演員Norman Reedus(曾參與電視劇《The Walking Dead》)一同出席。他們在其中一個舞台環節中，就電子遊戲與傳統電影的融合作出分享，當中小島提到關於《 Death Stranding 》的一些細節。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/003-3-e1556377348645.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F003-3-e1556377348645.jpg%3F&h=3ed3904c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>左方為演員Norman Reedus，右方為遊戲製作人小島秀夫</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>受真實世界所啟發的故事主題</strong><br />\n小島形容遊戲的主題是「連結(Connection)」，主角Sam(由Norman Reedus飾演)是一個十分孤獨和寂寞的人，而玩家需要努力地把這個世界重新再連結起來。他期望透過《Death Stranding》反映他對真實世界的體會，他認為互聯網的出現表面上打破國界，連接起不同地方的人；但同時亦有部份人正在築起圍牆，中斷與外界的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/009.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F009.jpg%3F&h=83e4a90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「連結」套用在遊戲玩法中</strong><br />\n演員Norman Reedus亦指《Death Stranding》與他兒子所玩的電子遊戲很不同，雖然作品中都有暴力環節，但並非單純殺光所有敵人。小島表示遊戲擁有一個開放世界，而他更賣關子：「我們加入了一個很新穎的元素，就是所有玩家都會連結起來，大家其實都在一起遊玩。但我現在還不能向大家解釋更多，否則Sony會很不高興，我不想失去我與Sony之間的『連結』。」或許這是對《Death Stranding》網絡連線部份的抽象描述？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/005-2.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F005-2.jpg%3F&h=4608924c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Norman Reedus施展混身解數</strong><br />\n由演員Norman Reedus擔任3D模組及動態捕捉的遊戲主角Sam，在作品中將會有不少施展個人魅力的機會。小島指出，當到了遊戲某一個特定場景，玩家會轉為操控鏡頭而非主角Sam。除了可以改變方向四處探索，當大家選擇望向Sam的時候，他則會對著鏡頭「單眼(wink)」。至於到了劇情環節，由Norman Reedus演繹的Sam會感動一眾電視機前的玩家。小島相信大家都會喜歡Norman的演出，甚至會因而成為他的粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/007.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F007.jpg%3F&h=4b26729d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/011.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F011.jpg%3F&h=d7fe6029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>這個「特定場景」會否是預告中曾出現，Sam可以洗澡休息的地方？</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一個多月後將有新發佈？</strong><br />\n最後，小島對於未能在活動上展示《Death Stranding》的成果感到抱歉，<span style=\"color: red;\">但他提到或許在一個多月後大家將會得到更多新情報。而一個多月後的6月份，剛好是一年一度的E3遊戲展。</span>雖然Sony已宣佈不會參加，但小島會否另外發佈新預告？畢竟在twitter上都能看到小島向不同人士展示《Death Stranding》的內容，相信他只是等待一個既得到Sony允許，又合適的時機而已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/004-2.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F004-2.jpg%3F&h=87864d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>圖左為電影導演Guillermo del Toro(代表作品《忘形水》)</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://greatgame.asia/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/008.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgreatgame.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F008.jpg%3F&h=949fbd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>圖左為電影導演Joel Coen(代表作品《二百萬奪命奇案》)</em>"},{"pid":"8438e285f01c3205826521133823de7a58cf1bd7","tid":1130146,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751672cfa8604f361878282ba76e4d13d6be3338","tid":1130146,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8438e285f01c3205826521133823de7a58cf1bd7","tid":1130146,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"演員Norman Reedus亦指《Death Stranding》與他兒子所玩的電子遊戲很不同，雖然作品中都有暴力環節，但並非單純殺光所有敵人。小島表示遊戲擁有一個開放世界 <br />\n<br />\n類似assassin's creed ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ea2627012e5ac0fc75fd55cb24cb5d77d439d7","tid":1130146,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"快啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d0c76a108778c4e78d83287fbc83a01a80065d","tid":1130146,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"Ps4玩到先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7e81d717e119a267d8a7f